[[File:StarkillerDeckplan-Challenge66.png|thumb|right|200px|The ''Starkiller'', a modified Frommon longhaul all-purpose transport]]
The '''Frommon longhaul all-purpose transport''' was one of the first [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]]-capable [[Freighter/Legends|freighters]] during the early years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], as was evidenced by their crude [[Ion coil engine|ion coils]]. It came in at 30 meters and required a crew of two people to operate it. One such ship, the ''[[Starkiller]]'', was used by [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Leshy Drobo]].

